From b22c07c00c073fb36c69ac6ef0c476d0663c7245 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Florent Revest <revestflo@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 2026 07:42:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] pri: Use Qt6 pkg-config module names

The libconnman-qt and libqofono dependencies were migrated to Qt6, which
renamed their pkg-config modules: connman-qt5 -> connman-qt6,
qofono-qt5 -> qofono-qt6 and qofonoext -> qofonoext-qt6. Update the .pri
to match, otherwise qmake fails do_configure with
'connman-qt5 development package not found'.

Upstream-Status: Pending
---
 geoclue-providers-hybris.pri | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/geoclue-providers-hybris.pri b/geoclue-providers-hybris.pri
index e4177e7..9bc5e5d 100644
--- a/geoclue-providers-hybris.pri
+++ b/geoclue-providers-hybris.pri
@@ -8,7 +8,7 @@ target.path = /usr/libexec
 QT = core dbus network
 
 CONFIG += link_pkgconfig
-PKGCONFIG += connman-qt5 qofono-qt5 qofonoext
+PKGCONFIG += connman-qt6 qofono-qt6 qofonoext-qt6
 
 LIBS += -lrt
 
-- 
2.47.3

